  "overview": {
    "zh": "XD系列振动筛是高效筛分设备，采用双轴激振器驱动系统，筛面积3-21m²，处理能力50-600m³/h。适用于2-50mm物料筛分，高精度分级，广泛应用于矿产、建材和冶金工业。",
    "en": "XD Series Vibrating Screen is a high-efficiency screening equipment featuring dual-shaft exciter drive system, 3-21m² screening area, and 50-600m³/h processing capacity. Ideal for 2-50mm material classification with high precision, widely utilized in mining, construction materials, and metallurgical industries."
  },
